&gt;&gt; Mary Sue Twohy:
When you heard a band

01:31:33.990 --> 01:31:37.740
at the Tonder Festival
in 2008, what was going

01:31:37.740 --> 01:31:39.070
on when you heard this band?

01:31:39.070 --> 01:31:40.560
&gt;&gt; Billy Bragg: I was walking
around the festival having a,

01:31:40.560 --> 01:31:42.610
trying to sauce out what
the audience might be

01:31:42.610 --> 01:31:45.180
like for my performance which
